            <text>Range of electromagnetic force is ____.</text>
            <option id="A">Infinite</option><option id="B">1 meter</option><option id="C">1 micrometer</option><option id="D">10^-15 m</option>
            <answer>A</answer><explanation>Like gravity, it has infinite range.</explanation>
