            <text>Energy and mass are related by ____.</text>
            <option id="A">E = mc^2</option><option id="B">E = 1/2 mv^2</option><option id="C">F = ma</option><option id="D">None</option>
            <answer>A</answer><explanation>Mass-energy equivalence.</explanation>
