            <answer>A</answer><explanation>Time is relative to observer.</explanation>
        </question>
        <question>
            <text>In quantum tunnelling, particle crosses ____.</text>
            <option id="A">Energy barrier higher than its own energy</option><option id="B">Ocean</option><option id="C">None</option><option id="D">D</option>
            <answer>A</answer><explanation>Forbidden in classical mechanics.</explanation>
        </question>
        <question>
            <text>Entanglement means particles are ____ regardless of distance.</text>
